    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Heart of Artemisa</strong> is a <strong>rhythm adventure game</strong>, with <strong>dungeon crawler &amp; Roguelite elements</strong>, where the player has to defeat enemies and solve puzzles <strong>at the beat of music</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game’s aesthetic has a <strong>retro 16-bit pixel art</strong> style and a mix of dancing and <strong>spooky music</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/extras/c2185fa65c0fb57930b7988768af86a5.poster.avif?t=1765426186\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/extras/c2185fa65c0fb57930b7988768af86a5.webm?t=1765426186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/extras/c2185fa65c0fb57930b7988768af86a5.mp4?t=1765426186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will explore a <strong>2D top down view world</strong> with caves and dark dungeons of the deep depths of a mysterious and cursed dungeon.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Movement and combat system are based on following the rhythm of the music</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This feature won’t be strict or obligatory. Players can proceed through the game without following the beat of music, but following the beat will make their adventure easier since the attacks will cause more damage to enemies. The more hits you do at the beat, more damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/extras/509ab94146055d8a028f3bffb7a24d9e.avif?t=1765426186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/extras_big/509ab94146055d8a028f3bffb7a24d9e.avif?t=1765426186 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
